data.description: Check out this beautiful brick home in Somerset, KY the CAPITAL OF LAKE CUMBERLAND. Located just minutes from EVERYTHING. Newly remodeled with hardwood floors. The large eat in kitchen provides plenty of countertops , food prep spaces and storage. HVAC and water heater are just years old. Chain link fence gives you a place for the children and pets to play with added security.  Drink coffee and watch the deer as you relax in your new home .Country living with privacy just minutes form all amenities.  Priced to SELL!
